Author: MadeinCoin
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: KubitX is a global hybrid digital asset exchange with focus on the emerging markets. Its built to be a one stop platform for the users. Many countries and citizens have been left behind in the blockchain revolution especially from Africa and hence we decided to make Africa as our first roll-out continent. We are hybrid as we plan to leverage on the technology behind the Blockchain to solve prevalent problems within Africa around payments (local and international), Trade Financing and Remittances. The KuBitX Ecosystem will support digital currency to fiat handshake to get transactions done using the TRANSPARENCY, SPEED, SECURITY AND IMMUTABILITY of the underlying technology.  Source; https://www.kubitx.io

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: There is whitelist for participation Please read below post.  Whitelisting To be guaranteed of a slot during the Public Round, users must be whitelisted. Whitelisting is open on our website https://kubitx.io (it is better to get a referral link from someone who already has one, when on the site, just click "JOIN TO CONTRIBUTE")   How to earn more KBX Each member who creates account on the TGE dashboard receives a unique referral link which he can share with friends and family. Remember to ask for a referral link from a registered participant to be able to get extra bonus.  Any member whose referral link is used by a referral to sign up and contribute to the TGE receives a bonus of 5% of the value of the contribution their referral makes.  Any new member who signs up and contributes to the TGE using a referral link receives a bonus of 3% of the value of their contribution for signing up using a referral link. (This is in addition to the bonus of the TGE Round they are participating in).  There is no limit to the number of people you can refer and there is no limit to the amount of KBX you can earn through your referral link.  The more people sign up through your link and contribute, the more KBX bonus you will earn.

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: Education is key for the adoption of cryptocurrency in our target market so we have the ambassadors initiative to enable us to reach the grassroots, using education to drive adoption of this new technology in those regions. Africa for example, is with a population of 1.2 billion, more than 60% of these people are unbanked. However more than 60% of this population has access to mobile telephony. We have also seen that some African countries rank among the most traders of cryptocurrencies in other exchanges, despite the fact that a few percentage of the population are aware of cryptocurrency, so we believe that coming out with an exchange that will not only give more Africans the opportunity to trade cryptocurrencies, but also provide them with other financial services to address the peculiar issue we have in Africa which we will use education to drive the adoption of will be a successful venture for us and our funders, so the upside potential is huge.

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: It is worthy of note that our token the KBX is a utility token. Apart from the trading fees which traders may prefer to pay with KBX token to get cheaper trading fees, we have other use cases for KBX.  Remittances Foreign immigrant workers from developing countries send a lot of  funds back to their home country with a view to help alleviate poverty conditions. As at 2016, US$ 442 billion was sent to developing countries through remittances alone. KuBitX can successfully capture even a small portion of the market (which will be easy through our strategic partnerships and the benefits the blockchain will have over existing options) this we will achieve using the KBX token.  Trade payments KuBitX will provide the opportunity for intra African trade payments to occur at a cheaper rate and faster using the KBX token, this will also increase the utility of the KBX token and increasing the upside potential for our funders.  Payment for goods and services KBX token will also be used for payment of goods and services for over 3000 merchants on our partners platform in Nigeria, which we have already acquired the APIs to connect to.  ETC.  Please check our product road map to see what we are offering https://kubitx.io/ProductRoadmap.pdf

Author: MaZeeCM
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: KuBitX has identified and reviewed the industry best practices in terms of security measures and designed our platform to include top level security features to safeguard both the client’s funds and trading operations from hostile penetration attempts. Some of the key security features include: - Multi-Factor authentication - All user data at rest are encrypted using the very strong encryption algorithm - Secure cold storage with cold wallet management Cryptocurrency Security Standard (CCSS) - KuBitX has developed a third-party code verification - GDPR compliant. - OWASP Top 10 Compliant & More. - Anti DDoS Protection - Web Application Firewall - Robust user’s account security - Defense in Depth Security for the platform etc. And other KuBitX customized security measures  Please check this write up showing how important security is for an exchange:  KUBITX CARES ABOUT YOUR SECURITY! Check the medium post https://medium.com/@kubitx/kubitx-cares-about-your-security-5272078c694d

Author: MaZeeCM
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: Please note that all cryptocurrencies are traded against the USD, and they each have a 3 or 4 letter ticker: BTC for Bitcoin, ETH for Ethereum, LTC for Litecoin, XRP for Ripple, DASH for Digital Cash, BCH for Bitcoin Cash, EOS for EOS.IO, OMG for OmiseGo, ZEC for Zcash, KBX for KuBitX, etc. Meanwhile, if you are referring on working with partners, yes, one is Modulus which is a partner and yes the trade engine is built by Modulus. Also the CEO of Modulus is our trade and exchange advisor, you may read this blog post https://medium.com/@kubitx/kubitx-modulus-a-unique-partnership-4edee53e9bd3 for your further reference. Meanwhile, KuBitX also partners with NEM and aims to build awareness around education in the emerging markets. This is one of the several partnerships we will also have.

Author: MaZeeCM
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: KuBitX has identified and reviewed the industry best practices in terms of security measures and designed our platform to include top level security features to safeguard both the client’s funds and trading operations from hostile penetration attempts. Some of the key security features include: - Multi-Factor authentication - All user data at rest are encrypted using the very strong encryption algorithm - Secure cold storage with cold wallet management Cryptocurrency Security Standard (CCSS) - KuBitX has developed a third-party code verification - GDPR compliant. - OWASP Top 10 Compliant & More. - Anti DDoS Protection - Web Application Firewall - Robust user’s account security - Defense in Depth Security for the platform etc. And other KuBitX customized security measures  Please check this write up showing how important security is for an exchange  KUBITX CARES ABOUT YOUR SECURITY! Check the medium post https://medium.com/@kubitx/kubitx-cares-about-your-security-5272078c694d

Author: STUNTMANMAJK
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: Are we talking about this?  NEM is a peer-to-peer cryptocurrency and blockchain platform launched on March 31, 2015. Written in Java, with a C++ version in the works, NEM has a stated goal of a wide distribution model and has introduced new features to blockchain technology such as its proof-of-importance (POI) algorithm, multisignature accounts, encrypted messaging, and an Eigentrust++ reputation system. The NEM blockchain software is used in a commercial blockchain called Mijin, which is being tested by financial institutions and private companies in Japan and internationally.  NEM technology allows multiple ledgers to coexist on one blockchain. Thanks to NEM Smart Assets users can create mosaics which can represent any asset (e.g. currency). All transactions in NEM have transaction fee associated with them and denomination used to pay for transactions is mosaic named XEM.

If you want to join and contribute, you will need to click on the contribute to the TGE button on the home page, and login to contribute. Once logged in, you will see the following information: 1. How much time is left until the current TGE phase is ended 2. How many KBX tokens per 1ETH 3. The current bonus 4. How much has been raised so far 5. How much is being raised.  Other information pertaining to the TGE. It seems pretty transparent and straight forward if you are an interested investor.

Author: nothingman19
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: They do have a plan. Answer to your question: Quote from: Cryptostruck on August 16, 2018, 02:22:47 PM Quote from: EFlo! on August 16, 2018, 01:40:40 PM Quote from: NelsonAv on August 15, 2018, 05:28:02 PM Quote from: GunMass on August 15, 2018, 04:25:01 PM Kubitx is currently based on ETH blockchain. Even though I am aware that ETH blockhain is really robust and actually a pretty good solution, I am still wondering when do you plan to implement your own blockchain?  I have noticed on your website that you plan to launch your on chain in the near future. What exactly does the “near future” mean?  We are expressing that there are plans for it. We hope you can follow our project for future progress and announcements.  what would be your plans regarding your own blockchain? For example if we compare your future blockchain with  ETH blockchain (which is robust and good as someone already stated), what would make your blockchain better than ETH? When ETH is compared to Bitcoin for example we already know the differences between these two. And what would your new blockchain offer us that is better than ETH blockchain?  KuBitX digital currency trading platform will be directly integrated with its financial services providers, allowing users a seamless experience when managing their accounts and buying/selling digital currencies and tokens. Also developers can design and build their applications knowing they will have no problem opening a financial services account for their business.

Body: All questions and discussion regarding the bounty campaign shall be carried out in the bounty campaign thread https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4632164  Quote from: dimaVODKA on August 17, 2018, 07:51:18 AM Quote from: MaZeeCM on August 17, 2018, 06:55:53 AM Quote from: johnwest on August 17, 2018, 06:18:25 AM How much Kubitx raised till now and whether there were some private sales in the beginning.? Would want to know the benefits of the token on the platform.  We have raised around 1M so far. We started with the Seed Round which we achieved the soft cap now we are currently running the Pre-Public round ( or private round, if you want to call it that way ). As for the KBX token, the KBX token will primarily be used to pay the trading fees in the KuBitX exchange platform. Execute other financial services product offering like payments, remittance and use cases stated in our whitepaper based on the roadmap  How much you plan to raise,whats your hard cap?  Our hardcap is 25,000 ETH

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: KUBITX REFERRAL PROGRAM  In order to encourage our community to participate more in our project, we have activated our referral program to reward those who will help us to spread the word about our project.  Each member who creates account on the TGE dashboard receives a unique referral link which he can share with friends and family.  Any member whose referral link is used by a referral to sign up and contribute to the TGE receives a bonus of 5% of the value of the contribution their referral makes.   Any new member who signs up and contributes to the TGE using a referral link receives a bonus of 3% of the value of their contribution for signing up using a referral link. (This is in addition to the bonus of the TGE Round they are participating in).  The referral link will be used during the Token Generation Event, both for Pre-Public and Public Rounds. There is no limit to the number of people you can refer and there is no limit to the amount of KBX you can earn through your referral link.  The more people sign up through your link and contribute, the more KBX you will earn.  We have put a guide together to ensure that our community understands the process of the TGE. Please follow the process to participate in our TGE. https://medium.com/@kubitx/kbx-token-generation-event-a-comprehensive-guide-250ae7e3e656

Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: KuBitX has identified and reviewed the industry best practices regarding security measures and designed our platform to include top-level security features to safeguard both the client’s funds and trading operations from hostile penetration attempts.  Some of the key security features include the following: - Secure cold storage with cold wallet management Cryptocurrency Security Standard (CCSS) - Third-party security line by line code audit by the NCC group - Insurance of online/hot wallets - Up to 3-Factor Authentication - Multi-Firewall Protection - DDoS prevention - OWASP Top 10 Compliant - Extended Validation SSL Certificate

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: KuBitX is incorporated in Malta, however, most of the founding members are Africans and others from various parts of the globe with strong professional background and influential organizational abilities with fortune 500 companies and big 4s. Motivation behind Malta, the Blockchain Technology which is the underlying technology of cryptocurrency is still new and most African countries have not initiated or instituted legal framework to make businesses on Blockchain work with clear order to shield the users, funding partners and stakeholders. In order not to sit tight for a really long time, the team had to sought for the most conducive clime to domicile the company where we will be compliant with law of commitment, Malta turned into the decision because of clear lawful system controlling setting up of Blockchain based organizations. We will work comprehensively with massive education to enable African decision makers comprehend and get the required administrative structure for easy operations of this unique business model.

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: KuBitX has identified and reviewed the industry best practices in terms of security measures and designed our platform to include top level security features to safeguard both the client’s funds and trading operations from hostile penetration attempts. Some of the key security features include: - Multi-Factor authentication - All user data at rest are encrypted using the very strong encryption algorithm - Secure cold storage with cold wallet management Cryptocurrency Security Standard (CCSS) - KuBitX has developed a third-party code verification - GDPR compliant. - OWASP Top 10 Compliant & More. - Anti DDoS Protection - Web Application Firewall - Robust user’s account security - Defense in Depth Security for the platform etc. And other KuBitX customized security measures  Please check this write up showing how important security is for an exchange  KUBITX CARES ABOUT YOUR SECURITY! Check the medium post https://medium.com/@kubitx/kubitx-cares-about-your-security-5272078c694d

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: As part of the KuBitX User Agreement, we verify the identity of all account holders conducting financial transactions. Withdrawals on the exchange are not permitted until this process is completed.  In order to have your account with us verified, you must send us the following documents from the email address you used to register with KuBitX exchange:  1) A valid, unexpired, government issued colour document with a photograph of you that contains your name and address or your name and date of birth such as a passport, a driver’s licence, birth certificate or Indian status card. Other than a passport, identity documents sent to us must have a scan of the front and the back.  2) A valid, unexpired, secondary identity document in colour such as a government issued driver’s licence, a government issued health card, or a credit card issued by a financial institution that contains your name and a signature on the back. The secondary identity document sent to us must have a scan of the front and the back.  3) A copy of a utility bill or statement from a financial institution in your name in colour that shows your name and address that is less than three months old.  4) A selfie of you holding your government issued identity product (item #1) in colour and a handwritten statement containing the word "KuBitX" that has been dated and signed . TIP: We require a clear image of the document as well as your entire face in this selfie. Be sure your camera lens is clean and be sure to steady your camera.  Please note that:  Your documents must be uncropped and unaltered or un-doctored to be accepted for identity verification by us.  You must use the email address you used to register your account with us. All documents must be in colour and in high resolution.  The KuBitX User Agreement which governs the terms of use of your account with KuBitX describes the terms of identity verification we undertake and they apply to your account and our services. The identity verification process applies to accounts at all times, including to close an account with us or to withdraw from an account. The verification process involves third party verification and may take some time.   We have the following categories of users:   Unverified You can look around, deposit, and trade unlimited digital currency. You can purchase BTC using a credit card but you may not withdraw from the exchange until you verify your identity.    Identity Verified You can deposit, trade, and withdraw digital and fiat currency.  This includes a face to face or digitally acceptable verification of your government issued ID. Further address, bank and income verification may be necessary to qualify for a trading account or limit increase.     Institutional Unlimited deposit, trading, and withdrawal limits in both fiat and digital currencies.  Business and director verification is required.  This includes a face to face or digitally acceptable verification of your government issued ID. Articles of incorporation, business license, director authorization and verification of bank account will be required.

KuBitX is making a stride in this direction and with its unique initiative called Global Channel Ambassadors to enter, understand and capture local emerging markets. We aim to tackle the socio-economic hindrances to adoption. The KuBitX Global Ambassador Initiative will reach the grassroots to drive local adoption.

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: Our fees are the lowest around, it is even lower when you choose to use our native token the KBX for fees payment.  Trading fee on KuBitX exchange is 0.05%, however, the users opting to use KuBitcoin(KBX) tokens as a method of payment of trading fee will get a discount of 25% compared to the original trading charges. - Trading fee = 0.05% - Trading fee using KBX token= 0.0375%  I would invite you to read our whitepaper all the information is already given there https://kubitx.io/KuBitX_Whitepaper_v1.1_En.pdf

Author: Obi2024
Title: [ANN][ICO] KUBITX - Cryptocurrency Exchange & Trading Platform
Body: We created an exchange because of Purpose. Our purpose to start was the people and the economy in the emerging markets We decided to create an exchange because exchanges will be the principal impetus for the transformation and significant change the Blockchain technology seeks to accomplish, especially in the emerging markets. It is anticipated that, in the coming years, all the sectors will have their own tokens hence the demand on exchange to give Transparent, Smart, Fast, Secure, Reliable and most straight forward methods for drawing in the groups will be high, our choice to be early adopters and push for mass appropriation with our one of a kind brand of giving mass adoption through education on the most proficient method to trade utilizing our platform.  The distinction between us and others will be our human way to deal with the business. We will in addition to other things give, transparency to exchanging, speed of transaction, security, responsive client support and a really worldwide trade regardless of geographic areas. Also our exchange will be a way to open up the emerging market economy which will help everyday people, the unbsnkef and underbanked. To do this we started with having the traditional financial services integrated from our start Advantages: - First Crypto Exchange with an in-built Financial Services Provision natively designed from scratch - Most advanced technology in trade engine development implemented - Fastest exchange in the world in terms of transaction persecond achieving above 12 million transactions per second with low latency of 40 nanoseconds - The security of our exchange is US department of defense grade. - Carefully built with regulatory compliance as key priority. KuBitX exchange is the most future ready and the most regulation ready exchange. - KuBitX has a sophisticated Anti Market Manipulation tool using Artificial intelligence and machine learning. - First Crypto Exchange with a unique product and  Initiative to keep the exchange close to the people by having a strong channel system to drive education and adoption for the emerging markets. - Support of users planned to be customized and higher budget allocated - Trade Exchange will be ready on or before the public round of TGE
